No. 662. George Westinghouse, Jr., et al., Petitioners, v. The New York Air Brake Company et al. April 16, 1906. Mr. George H. Christy and Mr. Samuel R. Betts for petitioners. Mr. Charles Neave and Mr. Wm. A. Jenner for respondents.

Petition for a writ of''certiorari to the United States Circuit Court of Appeals for the Second Circuit denied.
